  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Muotka Wilderness Lodge is on a full board basis.</p>
<p>Breakfast, lunch and dinner is included in within the package. Breakfast is buffet style with a variety of hot and cold options. Lunch is either picnic style around an open fire on excursions, or served at the main Lodge. Dinner is a hearty buffet style three course meal. The <span>menu is inspired by Lappish cuisine, the restaurant uses local ingredients following seasonal availability.</span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
